title: 821. Which Teams Will Win the Most Super Bowls Over the Next 5 Years?
itunes:title: 821. Which Teams Will Win the Most Super Bowls Over the Next 5 Years?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, Bucky gives his takeaways from the Jaguars' OTAs as he's currently in Jacksonville. Then, the guys do a draft where they pick which teams will win the most Super Bowls over the next 5 years. To wrap up the show, the duo answer listener questions.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
